originalText.text: Sunny organized an excellent lecture series at the standard hotel. Each lecture was memorable — the topics were fun and interesting, there were matching cocktails. The audience was always fun and full of creative people. Sunny does a great job curating an interesting event and creating great spaces for people to network.
